    "body": "Set gasPrice in network config to a number. The default is now 'auto' which only works after London hardfork. Setting hardfork in config to 'berlin' does not work.\r\n\r\nExample solution:\r\n```\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  networks: {\r\n    mumbai: {\r\n      url: `https://polygon-mumbai.infura.io/v3/${process.env.INFURA_KEY}`,\r\n      accounts: { mnemonic: process.env.MNEMONIC },\r\n      gasPrice: 8000000000, // default is 'auto' which breaks chains without the london hardfork\r\n    },\r\n    polygon: {\r\n      url: `https://polygon-mainnet.infura.io/v3/${process.env.INFURA_KEY}`,\r\n      accounts: { mnemonic: process.env.MNEMONIC },\r\n      gasPrice: 8000000000, // TODO: change this every deploy\r\n    },\r\n  },\r\n};\r\n```",
